  m_Name: Line_Opening_01
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Bonbibi.DialogueLine
  speaker: 0
  isNarration: 1
  text: The Sundarbans has two halves. Bonbibi watches over the human side, where
    woodcutters and honey gatherers have come for generations. On the other side,
    deeper than most people dare to go, Dokkhin Rai keeps watch over the wild heart
    of the forest. The arrangement is ancient. Both sides flourish because neither
    takes more than it is given!
